#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:847
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The <guilabel>View</guilabel> tab can be used to filter PSE. For example, "
#| "this feature allows you to explore the elements of the set time period. "
#| "This is great for getting a feel for how the PSE evolved over time, as "
#| "more and more elements were discovered. Choose <guimenuitem>Discovery "
